            <img class="_j_lazyload _j_needInitShare" style="height:453px;width:680px;background:#FCF2DC" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" data-src="https://n3-q.mafengwo.net/s11/M00/60/3C/wKgBEFpG2MWAFucTABCqug1fyI056.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-rt-src="https://n3-q.mafengwo.net/s11/M00/60/3C/wKgBEFpG2MWAFucTABCqug1fyI056.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1360%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-pid="277751132" alt="" />
        </a>
                    </div>
            <div id="_j_photo_277751134" data-seq="277751135" data-pid="277751134" class="add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem"  style="width:680px">
        <a target="_blank" style="display: block" href="/photo/12938/scenery_8148478/277751134.html">
            <img class="_j_lazyload _j_needInitShare" style="height:453px;width:680px;background:#FCF2DC" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" data-src="https://n2-q.mafengwo.net/s11/M00/60/3C/wKgBEFpG2MeAftxnAAzI0s8aIKU57.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-rt-src="https://n2-q.mafengwo.net/s11/M00/60/3C/wKgBEFpG2MeAftxnAAzI0s8aIKU57.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1360%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-pid="277751134" alt="" />
        </a>
                    </div>
            <p class="_j_note_content _j_seqitem" data-seq="276668820">
            南山寺是一座仿古盛唐风格居山面海大型寺院。整个气势恢宏，为<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/21536.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="中国" target="_blank">中国</a>５０年来<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/66306.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="新建" target="_blank">新建</a>最大道场，也是南国规模最大寺庙。园内景致与雕塑相协调，建筑与绿化相融合，既规整肃穆，又幽雅清净。名山、名寺、名僧，闪相辉映，相得益彰。仁王殿内供奉寺庙门神哼哈二将，明清后，这种殿式建筑逐渐演变成牌坊式建筑——山门。
        </p>
            <div id="_j_photo_277751139" data-seq="277751140" data-pid="277751139" class="add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem"  style="width:680px">
        <a target="_blank" style="display: block" href="/photo/12938/scenery_8148478/277751139.html">
            <img class="_j_lazyload _j_needInitShare" style="height:453px;width:680px;background:#FCF2DC" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" data-src="https://n3-q.mafengwo.net/s11/M00/60/3D/wKgBEFpG2MqAU2bWAAw1OSTiGgo74.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-rt-src="https://n3-q.mafengwo.net/s11/M00/60/3D/wKgBEFpG2MqAU2bWAAw1OSTiGgo74.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1360%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-pid="277751139" alt="" />
        </a>
                    </div>
            <div id="_j_photo_277751141" data-seq="277751142" data-pid="277751141" class="add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem"  style="width:680px">
        <a target="_blank" style="display: block" href="/photo/12938/scenery_8148478/277751141.html">
            <img class="_j_lazyload _j_needInitShare" style="height:453px;width:680px;background:#FCF2DC" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" data-src="https://n3-q.mafengwo.net/s11/M00/60/3D/wKgBEFpG2M2AJkT7ABLZh18WH5w65.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-rt-src="https://n3-q.mafengwo.net/s11/M00/60/3D/wKgBEFpG2M2AJkT7ABLZh18WH5w65.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1360%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-pid="277751141" alt="" />
        </a>
                    </div>
            <p class="_j_note_content _j_seqitem" data-seq="276669441">
            天王殿当中供奉天冠<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/17298.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="弥勒" target="_blank">弥勒</a>和两个侍者，两旁立护法神四大天王。天王殿两侧分别是钟楼和转轮藏。从天王殿穿过游廊，便可进入大雄宝殿，殿内供奉主尊为释迦牟尼佛、阿弥陀佛和药师佛，还有文殊、普贤、迦叶、阿难、帝释、梵天、两尊供养<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/144576.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="菩萨" target="_blank">菩萨</a>和十六罗汉塑像。
        </p>
            <div id="_j_photo_277751143" data-seq="277751144" data-pid="277751143" class="add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem"  style="width:680px">
        <a target="_blank" style="display: block" href="/photo/12938/scenery_8148478/277751143.html">
            <img class="_j_lazyload _j_needInitShare" style="height:453px;width:680px;background:#FCF2DC" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" data-src="https://b2-q.mafengwo.net/s11/M00/60/3E/wKgBEFpG2NCAb9IJABK6Lt1gXvg65.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-rt-src="https://b2-q.mafengwo.net/s11/M00/60/3E/wKgBEFpG2NCAb9IJABK6Lt1gXvg65.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1360%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-pid="277751143" alt="" />
        </a>
                    </div>
            <p class="_j_note_content _j_seqitem" data-seq="276669759">
            自古名寺出高僧，南山寺的方丈是86岁高龄的高僧新成大和尚，监院是<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/21536.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="中国" target="_blank">中国</a>佛教协会副会长明生法师
        </p>
            <div id="_j_photo_277751150" data-seq="277751151" data-pid="277751150" class="add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem"  style="width:680px">
        <a target="_blank" style="display: block" href="/photo/12938/scenery_8148478/277751150.html">
            <img class="_j_lazyload _j_needInitShare" style="height:453px;width:680px;background:#FCF2DC" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" data-src="https://n2-q.mafengwo.net/s11/M00/60/3E/wKgBEFpG2NWAGnHjABKdr5Y9nc834.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-rt-src="https://n2-q.mafengwo.net/s11/M00/60/3E/wKgBEFpG2NWAGnHjABKdr5Y9nc834.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1360%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-pid="277751150" alt="" />
        </a>
                    </div>
            <p class="_j_note_content _j_seqitem" data-seq="276669975">
            缘起<br />
《华严经•入法界品》曰：“于此南方有山名补怛洛迦，彼有<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/144576.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="菩萨" target="_blank">菩萨</a>名观自在”。彼<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/144576.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="菩萨" target="_blank">菩萨</a>有“长居<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/18142.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="南海" target="_blank">南海</a>愿”。故世称<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/18142.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="南海" target="_blank">南海</a>观音。由于<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/144576.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="菩萨" target="_blank">菩萨</a>住大悲行门，自在成就，广行方便，普现一切众生之前，乃至与其共居而成熟之，故观音道场普遍各地而特显于浙东<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/11534.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="普陀山" target="_blank">普陀山</a>，盖<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/144576.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="菩萨" target="_blank">菩萨</a>居于<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/18142.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="南海" target="_blank">南海</a>而应化于十方也。
        </p>
            <div id="_j_photo_277751155" data-seq="277751156" data-pid="277751155" class="add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem"  style="width:680px">
        <a target="_blank" style="display: block" href="/photo/12938/scenery_8148478/277751155.html">
            <img class="_j_lazyload _j_needInitShare" style="height:453px;width:680px;background:#FCF2DC" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" data-src="https://b2-q.mafengwo.net/s11/M00/60/3F/wKgBEFpG2NmAc7y_AAkK4Be8-oE43.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-rt-src="https://b2-q.mafengwo.net/s11/M00/60/3F/wKgBEFpG2NmAc7y_AAkK4Be8-oE43.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1360%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-pid="277751155" alt="" />
        </a>
                    </div>
            <div id="_j_photo_277751161" data-seq="277751162" data-pid="277751161" class="add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem"  style="width:680px">
        <a target="_blank" style="display: block" href="/photo/12938/scenery_8148478/277751161.html">
            <img class="_j_lazyload _j_needInitShare" style="height:453px;width:680px;background:#FCF2DC" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" data-src="https://c4-q.mafengwo.net/s11/M00/60/40/wKgBEFpG2NyADuJYAAzBcdNJTjw46.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-rt-src="https://c4-q.mafengwo.net/s11/M00/60/40/wKgBEFpG2NyADuJYAAzBcdNJTjw46.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1360%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-pid="277751161" alt="" />
        </a>
                    </div>
            <p class="_j_note_content _j_seqitem" data-seq="276670165">
            <a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/21536.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="中国" target="_blank">中国</a>南山在<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/12938.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="海南" target="_blank">海南</a>之滨，<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10030.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="三亚" target="_blank">三亚</a>南山即<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/144576.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="菩萨" target="_blank">菩萨</a>长居之补怛洛迦，大光明山也。故琼州历来即有观音出巡<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/18142.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="南海" target="_blank">南海</a>之说，南山侧望之东瑁西瑁二岛，相传即观音挑土之遗迹。唐天宝年间，律宗祖师鉴真和尚五次东渡<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10183.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="日本" target="_blank">日本</a>受阻，登陆南山，得观音护持，第六次东渡<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/64941.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="成功" target="_blank">成功</a>。其后，<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10183.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="日本" target="_blank">日本</a>遣唐僧东密祖师弘法大师西来求法，亦为台风阻至南山，得观音加持，经<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/11246.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="泉州" target="_blank">泉州</a>至长安求法成就。莲花为观音<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/144576.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="菩萨" target="_blank">菩萨</a>三昧耶形，其种子字为纥哩　，表诸法自性清净亦如人之肉团心，似八叶莲花，本体原自清净。《崖州志》载：“光绪六年（公元1881年），<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10030.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="三亚" target="_blank">三亚</a>鸭仔塘村（南<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/12976.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="山东" target="_blank">山东</a>南麓）忽自产莲花，叶甚茂，三年乃谢。光绪二十三年，复产，愈甚，至今愈茂”。由此可见南山与佛门之殊胜因缘也。&nbsp;
        </p>
            <div id="_j_photo_277751165" data-seq="277751166" data-pid="277751165" class="add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem"  style="width:680px">
        <a target="_blank" style="display: block" href="/photo/12938/scenery_8148478/277751165.html">
            <img class="_j_lazyload _j_needInitShare" style="height:453px;width:680px;background:#FCF2DC" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" data-src="https://n2-q.mafengwo.net/s11/M00/60/41/wKgBEFpG2N6AIP6eAA76oBHV38I98.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-rt-src="https://n2-q.mafengwo.net/s11/M00/60/41/wKgBEFpG2N6AIP6eAA76oBHV38I98.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1360%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-pid="277751165" alt="" />
        </a>
                    </div>
            <div id="_j_photo_277751168" data-seq="277751169" data-pid="277751168" class="add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem"  style="width:680px">
        <a target="_blank" style="display: block" href="/photo/12938/scenery_8148478/277751168.html">
            <img class="_j_lazyload _j_needInitShare" style="height:453px;width:680px;background:#FCF2DC" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" data-src="https://p3-q.mafengwo.net/s11/M00/60/41/wKgBEFpG2OCAcsldAAxhDQczTe823.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-rt-src="https://p3-q.mafengwo.net/s11/M00/60/41/wKgBEFpG2OCAcsldAAxhDQczTe823.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1360%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-pid="277751168" alt="" />
        </a>
                    </div>
            <p class="_j_note_content _j_seqitem" data-seq="276670525">
            “仁王门&nbsp;”相当于一般寺庙中的“<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/11251.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="三门" target="_blank">三门</a>”，内奉密迹金刚和那罗延金刚，是寺院的守护神，根据佛说仁王护国般若汉罗蜜多经的记载，两金刚因护持佛法有功被封为仁王，故南山寺因仿唐而不称为“<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/11251.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="三门" target="_blank">三门</a>”，而依两位金刚称为“仁王门”。&nbsp;
        </p>
            <div id="_j_photo_277751170" data-seq="277751171" data-pid="277751170" class="add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem"  style="width:680px">
        <a target="_blank" style="display: block" href="/photo/12938/scenery_8148478/277751170.html">
            <img class="_j_lazyload _j_needInitShare" style="height:453px;width:680px;background:#FCF2DC" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" data-src="https://c2-q.mafengwo.net/s11/M00/60/42/wKgBEFpG2OKAQHHoAApBLspal-075.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-rt-src="https://c2-q.mafengwo.net/s11/M00/60/42/wKgBEFpG2OKAQHHoAApBLspal-075.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1360%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-pid="277751170" alt="" />
        </a>
                    </div>
            <div id="_j_photo_277751174" data-seq="277751175" data-pid="277751174" class="add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem"  style="width:680px">
