            <div id="_j_photo_277751189" data-seq="277751190" data-pid="277751189" class="add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem"  style="width:680px">
        <a target="_blank" style="display: block" href="/photo/12938/scenery_8148478/277751189.html">
            <img class="_j_lazyload _j_needInitShare" style="height:453px;width:680px;background:#FCF2DC" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" data-src="https://n1-q.mafengwo.net/s11/M00/60/46/wKgBEFpG2POAX_VlABKQ22xlv2M44.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-rt-src="https://n1-q.mafengwo.net/s11/M00/60/46/wKgBEFpG2POAX_VlABKQ22xlv2M44.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1360%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-pid="277751189" alt="" />
        </a>
                    </div>
            <div id="_j_photo_277751191" data-seq="277751192" data-pid="277751191" class="add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem"  style="width:680px">
        <a target="_blank" style="display: block" href="/photo/12938/scenery_8148478/277751191.html">
            <img class="_j_lazyload _j_needInitShare" style="height:453px;width:680px;background:#FCF2DC" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" data-src="https://p4-q.mafengwo.net/s11/M00/60/46/wKgBEFpG2PWAOaksAA9U_8X3fxQ08.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-rt-src="https://p4-q.mafengwo.net/s11/M00/60/46/wKgBEFpG2PWAOaksAA9U_8X3fxQ08.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1360%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-pid="277751191" alt="" />
        </a>
                    </div>
            <p class="_j_note_content _j_seqitem" data-seq="277751382">
            “<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/63039.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="金堂" target="_blank">金堂</a>&nbsp;”即大雄宝殿，唐朝时称为“<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/63039.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="金堂" target="_blank">金堂</a>”，史出《佛祖统计》：东汉明帝“夜梦金人，感梦求法”的典故。大雄宝殿即是正殿，或称大殿。大雄是称赞释迦牟尼佛威德高上的意思。&quot;大雄&quot;表示佛的智慧、法力雄厚无边。这里主要供奉以空间为主的横三世佛，即中间&quot;娑婆世界教主释迦牟尼佛&quot;，结跏趺（读jiafu，盘腿而坐，脚背放在股上，是佛教徒的一种坐法）坐，这是佛说法相；左边&quot;东方净琉璃世界教主药师佛&quot;，结跏趺坐，左手持药器，右手施无畏印，表示佛在告诉众生，不要畏惧生死，佛的智慧能帮助众生战胜畏惧生死的烦恼；右边&quot;西方极乐世界教主阿弥陀佛&quot;（阿弥陀译成汉语为无量寿），结跏趺坐，手结弥陀定印，表示接引众生的意思。&nbsp;四周为十六尊罗汉。&nbsp;<br />
　
        </p>
            <div id="_j_photo_277751194" data-seq="277751195" data-pid="277751194" class="add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem"  style="width:680px">
        <a target="_blank" style="display: block" href="/photo/12938/scenery_8148478/277751194.html">
            <img class="_j_lazyload _j_needInitShare" style="height:453px;width:680px;background:#FCF2DC" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" data-src="https://p1-q.mafengwo.net/s11/M00/60/47/wKgBEFpG2PiADJKRABGFx6S-p2Q96.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-rt-src="https://p1-q.mafengwo.net/s11/M00/60/47/wKgBEFpG2PiADJKRABGFx6S-p2Q96.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1360%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-pid="277751194" alt="" />
        </a>
                    </div>
            <div id="_j_photo_277751199" data-seq="277751200" data-pid="277751199" class="add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem"  style="width:680px">
        <a target="_blank" style="display: block" href="/photo/12938/scenery_8148478/277751199.html">
            <img class="_j_lazyload _j_needInitShare" style="height:453px;width:680px;background:#FCF2DC" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" data-src="https://p1-q.mafengwo.net/s11/M00/60/48/wKgBEFpG2PuAMpxrAA7kIaR2WM898.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-rt-src="https://p1-q.mafengwo.net/s11/M00/60/48/wKgBEFpG2PuAMpxrAA7kIaR2WM898.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1360%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-pid="277751199" alt="" />
        </a>
                    </div>
            <p class="_j_note_content _j_seqitem" data-seq="277751322">
            释迦牟尼佛是佛教的教主，二千五百年前<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10182.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="印度" target="_blank">印度</a>释迦族的一位王子出家成佛，建立了佛教，所以称为释迦牟尼佛。释迦牟尼佛像有各种不同的姿式，主要的有两种：一种是结跏趺坐：左手横置左足上名为‘定印’，表示禅定的意思；右手直伸下垂，名为‘触地印’，表示释迦在成道以前的过去生中，为了众生牺牲自己的头目脑髓，这一切唯有大地能够证明，因为这些都是在大地上作的事。这种姿式的造像名为成道相。一种是结跏趺坐：是左手横置左足上，右手向上屈指作环形名为‘说法印’，这是说法相，表示佛说法的姿式。另外有一种立像，左手下垂，右手屈臂向上伸，这名为旃(zhan)檀佛像，传说是佛在世时<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10182.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="印度" target="_blank">印度</a>优填王用旃檀木按照佛的形容所作。下垂名‘与愿印’，表能满众生愿；上伸名‘施无畏印’，表能除众生苦。后来仿照此形象制作的也叫作旃檀佛像。&nbsp;
        </p>
            <div id="_j_photo_277751202" data-seq="277751203" data-pid="277751202" class="add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem"  style="width:680px">
        <a target="_blank" style="display: block" href="/photo/12938/scenery_8148478/277751202.html">
            <img class="_j_lazyload _j_needInitShare" style="height:453px;width:680px;background:#FCF2DC" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" data-src="https://p4-q.mafengwo.net/s11/M00/60/48/wKgBEFpG2P6AbvUaABNhp9KeOtA46.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-rt-src="https://p4-q.mafengwo.net/s11/M00/60/48/wKgBEFpG2P6AbvUaABNhp9KeOtA46.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1360%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-pid="277751202" alt="" />
        </a>
                    </div>
            <div id="_j_photo_277751205" data-seq="277751206" data-pid="277751205" class="add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem"  style="width:680px">
        <a target="_blank" style="display: block" href="/photo/12938/scenery_8148478/277751205.html">
            <img class="_j_lazyload _j_needInitShare" style="height:453px;width:680px;background:#FCF2DC" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" data-src="https://b1-q.mafengwo.net/s11/M00/60/48/wKgBEFpG2QCAK7mdABBsU_9Au5095.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-rt-src="https://b1-q.mafengwo.net/s11/M00/60/48/wKgBEFpG2QCAK7mdABBsU_9Au5095.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1360%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-pid="277751205" alt="" />
        </a>
                    </div>
            <p class="_j_note_content _j_seqitem" data-seq="277751310">
            一般多在释迦牟尼佛像旁塑有两位比丘立像，一年老，一中年，这是佛涅槃以后迦叶尊者继领徒众，后世称为初祖。迦叶涅槃以后，阿难尊者继领徒众，后世称为二祖。俗称释迦佛为如来佛。这是错误的，因为如来和佛同是一切佛的通称，并不能说明是某佛，<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/63538.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="比如" target="_blank">比如</a>称人为先生阁下不能说明是某人一样。&nbsp;<br />

        </p>
            <div id="_j_photo_277751209" data-seq="277751210" data-pid="277751209" class="add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem"  style="width:680px">
        <a target="_blank" style="display: block" href="/photo/12938/scenery_8148478/277751209.html">
            <img class="_j_lazyload _j_needInitShare" style="height:453px;width:680px;background:#FCF2DC" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" data-src="https://b3-q.mafengwo.net/s11/M00/60/4A/wKgBEFpG2QaAcwOQABH5dncfkS003.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-rt-src="https://b3-q.mafengwo.net/s11/M00/60/4A/wKgBEFpG2QaAcwOQABH5dncfkS003.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1360%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-pid="277751209" alt="" />
        </a>
                    </div>
            <p class="_j_note_content _j_seqitem" data-seq="277751274">
            据史志所载，、<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10030.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="三亚" target="_blank">三亚</a>南山即<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/144576.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="菩萨" target="_blank">菩萨</a>长居之“补怛洛迦”，有“大光明山”之称，故琼州历来即有观音出巡<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/18142.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="南海" target="_blank">南海</a>之说。南山侧望之东瑁西瑁二岛，相传即观音挑土老祖宗遗迹，唐天宝年间，律宗祖师鉴真曾五次东渡<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10183.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="日本" target="_blank">日本</a>受阻，登陆南山弘法，得观音<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/144576.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="菩萨" target="_blank">菩萨</a>护持，第六次东渡<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/64941.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="成功" target="_blank">成功</a>。
        </p>
            <div id="_j_photo_277751212" data-seq="277751213" data-pid="277751212" class="add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem"  style="width:680px">
        <a target="_blank" style="display: block" href="/photo/12938/scenery_8148478/277751212.html">
            <img class="_j_lazyload _j_needInitShare" style="height:1020px;width:680px;background:#FCF2DC" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" data-src="https://b3-q.mafengwo.net/s11/M00/60/4A/wKgBEFpG2QmAfzzdAApDgFZ1gNY36.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-rt-src="https://b3-q.mafengwo.net/s11/M00/60/4A/wKgBEFpG2QmAfzzdAApDgFZ1gNY36.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1360%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-pid="277751212" alt="" />
        </a>
                    </div>
            <p class="_j_note_content _j_seqitem" data-seq="277751271">
            《崖州志》载：“光绪六年（１８８１年），<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10030.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="三亚" target="_blank">三亚</a>鸭仔塘村（南<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/12976.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="山东" target="_blank">山东</a>南麓）忽自产莲花，叶甚茂，三年乃谢。光绪二十年，复产，愈产愈甚，至今愈茂。”由此可见南山与佛门之殊胜因缘。
        </p>
            <div id="_j_photo_277751214" data-seq="277751215" data-pid="277751214" class="add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem"  style="width:680px">
        <a target="_blank" style="display: block" href="/photo/12938/scenery_8148478/277751214.html">
            <img class="_j_lazyload _j_needInitShare" style="height:453px;width:680px;background:#FCF2DC" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" data-src="https://n3-q.mafengwo.net/s11/M00/60/4B/wKgBEFpG2QyAKOKWAA5pG0oXJ9I42.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-rt-src="https://n3-q.mafengwo.net/s11/M00/60/4B/wKgBEFpG2QyAKOKWAA5pG0oXJ9I42.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1360%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-pid="277751214" alt="" />
        </a>
                    </div>
            <div id="_j_photo_277751219" data-seq="277751220" data-pid="277751219" class="add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem"  style="width:680px">
        <a target="_blank" style="display: block" href="/photo/12938/scenery_8148478/277751219.html">
            <img class="_j_lazyload _j_needInitShare" style="height:453px;width:680px;background:#FCF2DC" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" data-src="https://b4-q.mafengwo.net/s11/M00/60/4B/wKgBEFpG2Q-AOAKhABXmRfHLWS044.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-rt-src="https://b4-q.mafengwo.net/s11/M00/60/4B/wKgBEFpG2Q-AOAKhABXmRfHLWS044.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1360%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-pid="277751219" alt="" />
        </a>
                    </div>
            <div id="_j_photo_277751224" data-seq="277751225" data-pid="277751224" class="add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem"  style="width:680px">
